 - 崇嚴事雲磊山大悲寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/author-ZuzXfGup2XR6D9EtGGYzeQ">Phạm Sư Mạnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/T%C3%A2n-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u/poem-CNHWFxSDZGhdGTab_IxqUg">Tân thướng đầu - 新上頭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/author-wyu82iSv-bH9msUkq5vWDQ">Hàn Ốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-H%E1%BB%97/T%C3%ADch-t%C3%ADch-di%C3%AAm-H%E1%BA%B1ng-li%E1%BB%85m-thi%C3%AAn-kim-ti%E1%BA%BFu/poem-Dcney4k4iMn8ZX5bLDlMMQ">Tích tích diêm - Hằng liễm thiên kim tiếu - 昔昔鹽－恒斂千金笑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-H%E1%BB%97/author-ZK21rLayK3mmuHkvR5sQcg">Triệu Hỗ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/V%E1%BB%8Dng-giang-l%C3%A2u-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-t%C3%A1c/poem-eNbUcM_SK4-rAwsPpFDXFg">Vọng giang lâu thượng tác - 望江樓上作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
